sys.monitoring.html#monitoring-event-LINE
    .. _PY_RETURN: https://docs.python.org/3/library/\
sys.monitoring.html#monitoring-event-PY_RETURN
    .. _PY_YIELD: https://docs.python.org/3/library/\
